rComments: He just does whatever is given in the book. The class isn't bad. His hearing is very good so he always tells people to stop talking every 5 min even when most of the other students don't hear anything. I'm more than 10 years younger than him, and his hearing is way better than mine.

Although his second Language is English, and you can tell, he does make an effort to articulate well and is much appreciated. Definitely better than average math professor. Overall, Id' take him if the best profs classes are full.
